title: Piano Keyboard Note Labels Removable Piano Keyboard Stickers for Beginner Silicone Piano Notes Guide for Learning, 61-Key Full Size, No Need Stickers, Reusable and Comes with Box (61-Key Colorful)
features: Design for 61/88-key piano and keyboard, covering a full range of note,pitch marks,solfege (do re mi) and double staffs to help learn piano.

These non-sticky silicone piano stickers can be laid on the piano keyboard directly and can be removed or replaced at any time without leaving any adhesive residue on the keys like some piano stickers.
This piano keyboard helper covers a span of four octaves and is designed to work only with 88/61-key keyboards, such as pianos, electric keyboard pianos, and electric organs.
This keyboard sticker allows beginners to quickly remember the position of piano keyboard notes to improve their learning speed.

Please note that non-standard sized keyboards (76/54/49/37 keys) may not fit properly. Before purchasing, please confirm the size of the width of the gap between the top of the black keys and the keyboard case, which must be greater than 2.4 millimeters (0.1 inches).
